&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">&Aacute;nh s&aacute;ng trực tiếp</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: G&acirc;y phai m&agrave;u b&igrave;a s&aacute;ch, gi&ograve;n giấy.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">C&ocirc;n tr&ugrave;ng</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: Mối mọt, gi&aacute;n c&oacute; thể ph&aacute; hủy s&aacute;ch.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Bụi bẩn, dầu mỡ</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: L&agrave;m s&aacute;ch bị bẩn, giảm tuổi thọ.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">C&aacute;ch sắp xếp kh&ocirc;ng đ&uacute;ng</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: L&agrave;m g&atilde;y g&aacute;y s&aacute;ch, cong v&ecirc;nh trang giấy.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 26.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt;\">2. C&aacute;ch Bảo Quản S&aacute;ch V&agrave; Truyện Đ&uacute;ng C&aacute;ch</span></h2>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18.0pt;\">a. Bảo quản theo m&ocirc;i trường</span></h3>\r\n<h3><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://images.deepai.org/art-image/219a26e8f6f54a858f66db671c7dfbe1/generate-an-image-of-books-being-stored-in-a-dry-cool.jpg\" width=\"539\" height=\"539\" /></h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Tr&aacute;nh nơi ẩm ướt</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: Bảo quản s&aacute;ch ở nơi kh&ocirc; r&aacute;o, tho&aacute;ng m&aacute;t. C&oacute; thể d&ugrave;ng t&uacute;i h&uacute;t ẩm hoặc m&aacute;y h&uacute;t ẩm nếu cần.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Hạn chế &aacute;nh nắng trực tiếp</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: Kh&ocirc;ng để s&aacute;ch gần cửa sổ hoặc dưới &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng mạnh để tr&aacute;nh phai m&agrave;u.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Giữ nhiệt độ ổn định</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: Nhiệt độ l&yacute; tưởng l&agrave; 18-22&deg;C.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18.0pt;\">b. C&aacute;ch sắp xếp s&aacute;ch đ&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch</span></h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"https://images.deepai.org/art-image/e493e583ed6d43ea866