-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">D&ugrave;ng gi&aacute; s&aacute;ch chắc chắn</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">: Đảm bảo kh&ocirc;ng bị đổ hoặc g&acirc;y &aacute;p lực l&ecirc;n s&aacute;ch.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18.0pt;\">c. L&agrave;m sạch s&aacute;ch định kỳ</span></h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">D&ugrave;ng khăn mềm lau bụi thường xuy&ecirc;n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Tr&aacute;nh d&ugrave;ng tay ướt hoặc bẩn khi đọc</span><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">D&ugrave;ng hộp đựng s&aacute;ch hoặc bọc ni l&ocirc;ng cho s&aacute;ch qu&yacute;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 18.0pt;\">d. Ph&ograve;ng chống c&ocirc;n tr&ugrave;ng</span></h3>\r\n<h3><img src=\"https://images.deepai.org/art-image/7b63f4c2f51c4e5d9dd2134e44a7deee/generate-an-image-of-someone-using-a-soft-cloth-to-du.jpg\" width=\"714\" height=\"714\" /></h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">D&ugrave;ng long n&atilde;o hoặc t&uacute;i thơm<strong> để đuổi c&ocirc;n tr&ugrave;ng.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Vệ sinh kệ s&aacute;ch định kỳ<strong> để tr&aacute;nh bụi v&agrave; thức ăn thừa thu h&uacute;t c&ocirc;n tr&ugrave;ng.</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">Tr&aacute;nh ăn uống gần s&aacute;ch<strong> để kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;m rơi vụn thức ăn.</strong></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 26.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt;\">3. C&aacute;ch Kh&ocirc;i Phục S&aacute;ch Bị Hư Hỏng</span></h2>\r\n<h2><img src=\"https://images.deepai.org/art-image/d642150ed54e44afa78ae1aa907fbe68/generate-an-image-of-different-methods-to-restore-dam.jpg\" width=\"710\" height=\"710\" /></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">S&aacute;ch bị ẩm, mốc</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">: Phơi ở nơi kh&ocirc; r&aacute;o, d&ugrave;ng giấy h&uacute;t ẩm giữa c&aacute;c trang.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">S&aacute;ch bị quăn m&eacute;p</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">: Đặt dưới vật nặng trong v&agrave;i ng&agrave;y.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">S&aacute;ch bị r&aacute;ch</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">: D&ugrave;ng keo d&aacute;n giấy chuy&ecirc;n dụng hoặc băng d&iacute;nh trong suốt để sửa chữa.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&middot;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">S&aacute;ch bị bẩn</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">: D&ugrave;ng g&ocirc;m trắng hoặc khăn mềm lau nhẹ nh&agrave;ng.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 26.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 18.0pt;\">Kết Luận</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 28.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">B</span><span style=\"font-size: 16.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt;\">ảo quản s&aacute;ch v&agrave; truyện đ&uacute;ng c&aacute;ch gi&uacute;p k&eacute;o d&agrave;i tuổi thọ, giữ g&igrave;n tri thức cho thế hệ sau. H&atilde;y chăm s&oacute;c bộ sưu tập s&aacute;ch của bạn bằng những phương ph&aacute;p đơn giản nhưng hiệu quả tr&ecirc;n nh&eacute;! </span></p>', '2025-03-02 11:56:23');

